Name: My Car
About the game: Choose from one of two different car models! Customize it in your own way, then try it on the track! You will have the choice between a hundred different pieces. They can change the appearance of your car, but also the performance of the engine and suspension! The car is completely removable, each piece can be replaced, modified or removed! Change the patterns and colors of your car! A large map fully accessible with a track and different stunt ramp to try the performance of your racing car! Not to mention an excellent playlist of music! Features : ■ Two different car models! ■ Very complete system of customization with no less than 100 different pieces! ■ System to change the patterns and color of your car! ■ A large, fully accessible map! ■ A circuit in the middle of the map! ■ A multitude of stunt ramp! ■ Gearbox system and meter in km / h of the car! ■ Good music!
